Package com.dkamakin.s3.stream.impl

Class MultiPartInputStream

java.lang.Object
java.io.InputStream
com.dkamakin.s3.stream.impl.MultiPartInputStream
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, AutoCloseable
@NotThreadSafe public class MultiPartInputStream extends InputStream
Allows you to download files from S3 without the need to know file size, caching or storing the entire object in the file system. The stream downloads each part using GetObjectRequest.range() option. This class remembers the amount of read bytes and moves the pointer ByteRange. EOS considered as a 416 HTTP code got from S3. A new instance can be built using builder(). See also IMultiPartInputStreamBuilder
